# ============================================================================
#  WARNING: THIS FILE IS NOT APPLIED IN PRODUCTION. Read before trusting it.
#  This site deploys as a Cloudflare WORKER (see wrangler.toml [assets]), not
#  Cloudflare Pages. `_headers` is a Pages-only feature and is SILENTLY IGNORED
#  by Workers static assets.
#  Verified 2026-07-02: the LIVE response headers do not match this file — live
#  `font-src` lacks 'self', Permissions-Policy differs, HSTS has no 'preload'.
#  The live security headers come from a Cloudflare DASHBOARD rule
#  (Rules -> Transform Rules -> Modify Response Header, getsmartai.ai zone) and
#  MUST be edited there. This file is kept only as the intended spec; sync it by
#  hand, or migrate headers into the Worker so the repo owns them.
#  CRITICAL: the dashboard CSP must include  font-src 'self'  — without it the
#  self-hosted /fonts/*.woff2 are CSP-blocked and the whole site falls back to
#  system fonts.
# ============================================================================
/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains; preload
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=(), payment=(), usb=()
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://static.cloudflareinsights.com; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com; img-src 'self' data:; connect-src 'self' https://cloudflareinsights.com; frame-ancestors 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self'; object-src 'none'; upgrade-insecure-requests
